{"tid":2478481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講兩句 想時間快啲過 (85)","createTime":"2021-04-07T05:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:22:09.000Z","uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b8e419ca2335e56c84a48a5405b93145cf5c22","tid":2478481,"uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"依個post係俾失眠 失戀 想吐苦水 傾心事嘅人圍爐<br />\n<br />\n多謝上幾個post陪過我 俾過意見我嘅咁多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個post 除咗係圍爐取暖 <br />\n大家都可以入嚟吹下水 發下癲<br />\n分享一下去嗰邊 做咗啲乜嘢 <br />\n除咗擺低自己心事 都可以散播正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩開心野想分享都可以返嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKai子！窮！雪！多疑絲！ 大粒麥！跟我來巴！<br />\nCylmomt！辣油！可能巴！塵埃！Gary！<br />\n戒賭！宋文德！唔好玩絲！擱淺絲！成熟巴！<br />\n旅行巴！因緣巴！洞洞丸！別姫！茄豆！金太！<br />\n獵豹絲！毒計巴！離巴！喬！<br />\n已讀！中薯！PHY！本澤馬！貓狗！<br />\n雪花非花！風絲！教授！<br />\n仲有好多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗚 越來越多人唔係記得好清楚<br />\n如果你成日留名 但係我唔記得加你個名嘅話對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨便插嘴is okay<br />\n依度無規矩的 free~<br />\n當然發表意見要考慮對方感受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2aebc5b8c9fd33637c53bfc8b4ffab0def0516","tid":2478481,"uid":34706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"71ac923aac8b0f7d35e0fe81e9cd3cc6634df687","tid":2478481,"uid":209746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"33c6b8893a9653850eef89b417248295ca455227","tid":2478481,"uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"無人提我嘅<img src=\"/asset